{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_af543fb198b61388480dc5c1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "可能导致无障碍（accessibility）问题的另一类内容是多媒体——视频、音频和图像内容需要提供适当的文本替代方式，以便辅助技术及其用户能够理解它们。本文展示了具体内容。",
        "text_hash": "acef0d83af2236121070f129dbe49b7ac59dfe79b6446ad1e8fc627a21b5ae3d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c60c63fbb4274faeea9ee862",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "先决条件：",
        "text_hash": "86496acc5f4452bae88964bc2a6abc05548c85dbe27686b6c9c50f680561d853",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ad24d95661d5a86034337cff",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "基本的计算机素养，对 HTML，CSS 和 JavaScript 的基本理解， 对无障碍\n        的理解。",
        "text_hash": "ed06f5a144a5f4119d03ee53357a3a2987c074fd4bf3b8f8b0cb76ef5861f5cb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_187e666cc8dbbc34e5527dbc",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "目标：\n       了解多媒体背后的无障碍问题，以及如何克服这些问题。",
        "text_hash": "9669ece9963d0b26f9d18ca09fd0beae0f0143f0104ca2aae65b56e22a12f8a6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6a2e5effdf3fe1752ec0aeea",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "多媒体和无障碍",
        "text_hash": "1f80dbc6c95a898a87bab5c748c8bf5e91e1daf67b7d45161eaef21fe61eb59c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9579ca354a89dbe09fd26846",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "到目前为止，在这个模块中，我们已经查看了各种内容以及需要做些什么来确保其无障碍，从简单的文本内容到数据表，图像，本机控件（如表单元素和按钮）以及更复杂的标记结构（具有WAI-ARIA属性）。",
        "text_hash": "2010b164dc27dfa19a1567a785f0543fc82bb3b3269a8f2ccb1e7760eac6f193",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9beb039a285002e24c4a1a63",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "另一方面，这篇文章着眼于另一个一般的内容类别，可以说它不容易确保对多媒体的无障碍。图像，视频， 元素，Flash 电影等不易被屏幕阅读器理解或被键盘导航，我们需要帮助他们。",
        "text_hash": "fbac557cedaa2763d324c398d6abc757ebcc601a892c842048f7300467a1bd49",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5717f67869b709a2241a9df4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "但不要绝望 - 在这里我们将帮助你浏览可用于使多媒体更容易访问的技术。",
        "text_hash": "f6292389b033bc76eb0d6ab1e98d8b3551e81364bfb939d09d2f0e46694bd3b4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b39b8f2d489cb852703d4fd0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "简单图像",
        "text_hash": "1fb00d80089505ae2194a1fe2480e9752a8885173764e68cfaf256e48833cc38",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b389b75e2a0bdde516609f66",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我们已经介绍了 HTML 图像的简单文本替代HTML: A good basis for accessibility –– 你可以参考其中了解详细信息。简而言之，应确保在可能的情况下，视觉内容具有替代文本，供屏幕阅读器拾取和读取给其用户。",
        "text_hash": "2ff2f020f182bba4e4b6f845d5491517367d5bd27c230c78a9395b8d9516fe38",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1d65cfe1b62eca847e6c78ab",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "示例：",
