    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0cefaaa35330ceb86d2491a5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "但是，这些控件存在问题：",
        "text_hash": "63fbb91a8afdc7e5c42d4c97eb6c85244a9a62d7dd44d65e11bacea4c61e5294",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_067248c115ac290df3286b65",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在除 Opera 以外任何浏览器中，它们不可通过键盘访问。\n不同的浏览器为原生控件提供了不同的样式和功能，且不可赋予它们样式，这意味着它们难以遵从网站样式指南。",
        "text_hash": "b59a97210b51a53c5e9a6bbd6df93abd0fc5078403f6a6664bf131aca5b5f252",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ff7debceae0835a8f7d6ce93",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "为了解决这个问题，我们可以创建自己的自定义控件。让我们来看看如何。",
        "text_hash": "420a0075ff8f8f92956d81ca1895cec9e5888a3e296867807b3ef17985656190",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_26be3408a5302af80cc860d1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "创建自定义音频和视频控件",
        "text_hash": "dd1f9cbe2f9179ab26846a7d8953b200051b4c51e88afd90e9a5c9e0a5f5c214",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b14e2b1658d6cfdc47122da1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "HTML5 视频和音频共享 API — HTML Media Element — 允许你将自定义功能映射到按钮和其他控件––这两个控件都是你自己定义的。",
        "text_hash": "5020aa9deffd1917f8902cc1e6394af3fcce1a5dcd26fa27702f5bd8c8a6c6a9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5c7443c300c69f5be7a4393b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "让我们从上面获取视频示例，并向其添加自定义控件。",
        "text_hash": "56de63a7cb0d1f30f2e40a7581f26fcc522372907148c2d05b30f7afe4a2486c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f4ceb67ab54236a9d3fe644a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "基本设置",
        "text_hash": "f3f905f2853a4dbaaa4857833dd957d812c8cda9899ceb3c69421d383c420194",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d02535d18009ff5491d624e9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "首先，获取我们的custom-controls-start.html、custom-controls.css、 rabbit320.mp4 和 rabbit320.webm文件的副本，并将它们保存在硬盘上的新目录中。",
        "text_hash": "3f2507c797baa077648aecbecfa65d75904f26d087a33a54e880d305e8d8b6e8",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fdcbc90679c6ed98c56fec29",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "创建一个名为 main.js 的新文件并将其保存在同一目录中。",
        "text_hash": "1e70dd79d18497bea04ae75b266954e8433ed69d7ed13a91d32483e19c837a43",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c2b6eff49a4b8c54bf226dc5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "首先，让我们在 HTML 中查看视频播放器的 HTML:",
        "text_hash": "6c47a1fb6749cfc976697f33baf97854cbf8088d0d92ff997a07948da0b1dc6f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_94ae78dcf80f02a29181446b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "html",
        "text_hash": "e5e239560bc125a20ff2ac1fea50915bc198dd4f5b5256ec447a8a71e00132b3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_877a6966893df2727be3e17c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Your browser doesn't support HTML5 video. Here is a\n       link to the video  instead.",
        "text_hash": "8185d7a34d99e7d7ce6ba89f3053e29d61961ae786377102392dec76f5e3a2d4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
