      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Play\n     Stop\n     Rwd\n     Fwd\n     00:00",
        "text_hash": "338f09612504c0ca1e78074039f4a1be3c91ea3f5f07bec86a34c29ae0d4c394",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ca125fefcef49661d8944002",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "JavaScript 基本设置",
        "text_hash": "57ff2f770bc3b6abd72b1bbfa849ca57da295dab070ee6cc146cac00473923c2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a542f40ee8ec1b9d6140b692",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我们在视频下方插入了一些简单的控制按钮。当然，这些控件在默认情况下不会执行任何操作。要添加功能，我们将使用 JavaScript。",
        "text_hash": "1a7be2dcba103a134db10c1cfb25f9a23cfc97cd69befee285e614ceaa74b565",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_49d465314d073f1ea66ed7f9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我们首先需要存储对每个控件的引用––将以下内容添加到 JavaScript 文件的顶部：",
        "text_hash": "7897e92f1556759b8c2b2a7e3da9c193913b84e385ff498f7c64fc9ee91b884e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_baa9940bac4f6c86b2ef612c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "js\nconst playPauseBtn = document.querySelector(\".playpause\");\nconst stopBtn = document.querySelector(\".stop\");\nconst rwdBtn = document.querySelector(\".rwd\");\nconst fwdBtn = document.querySelector(\".fwd\");\nconst timeLabel = document.querySelector(\".time\");",
        "text_hash": "b5d10eb3fa7b50bb86bb5f9546b60cc5b90f448e5ff4cfab6f0d4936412fd082",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e2e0c451d75baf918de67cc7",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "接下来，我们需要获取对视频/音频播放器本身的引用––在前面的代码行下方添加此行代码：",
        "text_hash": "4e6ec1683a0688f9bdeaf02feca72e5607bd7e08768c527f9262b3cdf7b3bf91",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7b0a6a6bdfe887196f09fb04",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "js\nconst player = document.querySelector(\"video\");",
        "text_hash": "61f558f06e9da761788b5de9be1985b60e8eb49d5433d392e508ccc02e850406",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_638c31a2fde485ca797cc841",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这包含对对象的引用，该对象具有几个有用的属性和方法，可用于将功能连接到我们的按钮。",
        "text_hash": "d48652939448986217621852fca078062efa3371b45cee8af4d3865695a11e1e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d69ecc2955fd711ed27791b6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在开始创建按钮功能之前，让我们删除本地控件，以免它们妨碍我们的自定义控件。在 JavaScript 的底部再次添加以下内容：",
        "text_hash": "dd2f835718a321275e7ab2335538abcb998f2e4ba007cc62f7f4cc99b4bc16e7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7095f887605806ebf1503d4d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "js\nplayer.removeAttribute(\"controls\");",
        "text_hash": "1a9ad220b9ffa2e116ecd070ebf4d3cc5464f3894377044bc7fc58c90146f6d2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a0ec94682232b6056554b6af",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这样做，而不是仅仅不包括控件属性摆在首位有一个优势，如果我们的 JavaScript 失败，用户仍然有一些控件可用。",
        "text_hash": "5a4999fe43568b0a24b7ba247d6d45f6568913f602a6c62c31452f95cd1b95e0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5821b6a42bc1e7b775bd3849",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "连接按钮",
        "text_hash": "d3b71cc875f969cfc728f0c9d5304ce49ca5f2635acd1c3ffec38873691178d2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d031b6c4843f0e3697377b97",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "首先，让我们设置播放/暂停按钮。我们可以使用一个简单的条件函数在播放和暂停之间切换，如下所示。将其添加到代码底部：",
        "text_hash": "5557b9db323782f1be819129f35d4f5197a8b11ff5e2b6a6e8b6cabe51930213",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2cbbbe3ccc56433a6c1652a7",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "js\nplayPauseBtn.onclick = () => {\n  if (player.paused) {\n    player.play();\n    playPauseBtn.textContent = \"Pause\";\n  } else {\n    player.pause();\n    playPauseBtn.textContent = \"Play\";\n  }\n};",
        "text_hash": "2e9cb1aafa13c15b5fa3ceebb6191b9d48d1dc408c87c6eee63135a80bc1f068",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8794c5d3b4b29ed7d7f369d6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "接下来，将此代码添加到底部，该代码控制停止按钮：",
        "text_hash": "e2fa2e94047754a87bd0075b7f95ca58b1cd12721da3edacdf43331ce823e121",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d47a2fc2d448518c3d04ab9e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "js\nstopBtn.onclick = () => {\n  player.pause();\n  player.currentTime = 0;\n  playPauseBtn.textContent = \"Play\";\n};",
        "text_hash": "76a9f5e2de23aebe823fe41a8182087c5a810f36ad57391b1d314b64e06cb7d3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_773e154bd1cd48dee1ed080f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在  上没有可用的 stop() 函数，因此我们改为pause()它，同时将当前时间设置为 0。",
        "text_hash": "e12b4e7557433cb02e957135baf4af5c37266efd4eac4b89b46deb3c933aad13",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a7101901e38169832950d79d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "接下来，我们的快退和快进按钮–– 将以下块添加到代码的底部：",
        "text_hash": "47a8bba71e5ec7f04e274b593e7d58fcde0fb2ae7642e01951e2603ccee5ec7f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_847205135d7bb93e1f909ff9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "js\nrwdBtn.onclick = () => {\n  player.currentTime -= 3;\n};",
        "text_hash": "9228b1371be23ea3b71c0522700b44f75073bceb0b92321d30c40fab060a6682",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e60828c5f4c0751e733b8c43",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "fwdBtn.onclick = () => {\n  player.currentTime += 3;\n  if (player.currentTime >= player.duration || player.paused) {\n    player.pause();\n    player.currentTime = 0;\n    playPauseBtn.textContent = \"Play\";\n  }\n};",
        "text_hash": "562a88802b2ada73824e63520e8449bdd7b540ea887ae4ea7b21a1afdc36c26e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_abe6efc8c2813756ed2a52e1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这些非常简单，每次单击它们时，只需将 3 秒添加到currentTime。在真正的视频播放器中，你可能想要一个更精细的查找栏或类似功能。",
        "text_hash": "0d04cb253f9f928fd36aff519b26921aa8ee7f6a33cfaa95e48b481b19dda0cb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a4007f0afede8cdbb1bd386a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "请注意，当按下 Fwd 按钮时，我们还会检查currentTime是否超过总媒体的duration,或者媒体是否未播放。如果任一条件为 true，我们只需停止视频，以避免用户界面出错，如果他们试图在视频未播放时快进，或快进通过视频结束。",
        "text_hash": "10f857ed85ed6eb341eb48c0949eb623c87e5309fd3996e931226d7fdbadbca3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1a214585c28483d2c784f5a3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "最后，将以下内容添加到代码末尾，以控制显示的时间：",
        "text_hash": "4658f7fd683343e6d3d38bff7cb438e9a34eb50ec8e0c9434d82a4ed67f32a4b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_98e32556d1f6e2c3dc24174e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "js\nplayer.ontimeupdate = () => {\n  const minutes = Math.floor(player.currentTime / 60);\n  const seconds = Math.floor(player.currentTime - minutes * 60);\n  const minuteValue = minutes   Transcript_\"。",
        "text_hash": "a4ebc98f16e393fffd55f8066147f8c45389e12684644e9b20165d6b5df337c7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8b584fb15d0db9b36ed326f5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "如果要创建自己的用户界面来显示音频和相关脚本，你可以随心所欲地执行此操作，但将其包含在可显示/可隐藏面板中可能有意义;请参阅我们的audio-transcript-ui 示例（另请参阅其源码）。",
        "text_hash": "93d711657d5e7d03a511fd041c7f98946c8021738a52b99d4c3df5eea917b845",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d6fa1d83170b90b101f12fe8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "音频描述",
        "text_hash": "6ea5362cfdbce7c526b032a7aa9a7fa38aad712bb8bc3eddaf3ad17515f6bb8c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_786e2ea28ec9098fe3d79944",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在音频附带视频的情况下，你需要提供某种音频说明来描述该额外内容。",
        "text_hash": "c26d69dee17140066558cd9d4f32c5a69a9d27996636e74f90ede423691a3710",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e7a454c2f68551e73fc8c516",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在许多情况下，这只会采取视频的形式，在这种情况下，你可以使用本文下一节中介绍的技术实现字幕。",
        "text_hash": "99535a9900859a7da0fcbcbd1b7e123566c27fb1d695d8a547e67d634ea8fc6e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8981730dc96528911b8ae097",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "但是，有一些边缘情况。例如，你可能有一个会议的音频录制，该录音引用了附带的资源，如电子表格或图表。在这种情况下，应确保资源与音频和脚本一起提供，并在成绩单中提及它们的位置专门链接到这些资源。这当然会帮助所有用户，而不仅仅是聋人。",
        "text_hash": "3465a687d1b82ab408736928a2a5e5fcf98c4fd30e894310ebdb8519aafb2d16",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2ad514cb77d96a12f247d639",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "[!NOTE]\n音频脚本通常有助于多个用户组。除了让聋人用户访问音频中包含的信息外，还考虑一个带宽连接较低的用户，他们会发现下载音频不方便。还要考虑在嘈杂的环境中 (如酒吧或酒吧) 中的用户，他们试图访问信息，但无法通过噪音听到信息。",
        "text_hash": "a34bd28a1e5579df058affbc2a17542acd6a543e7e9cc953b979576f3888c4f3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "quotation"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4c637d2abef32afad9d4bed4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "视频文本轨道",
        "text_hash": "6878797c499e024673f8a5788caf580c85034ef524351f37691c1ed796a2daf3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_76ebf8620b4333b19db62d1f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "要使聋人、盲人甚至其他用户组 (如低带宽用户或不理解视频录制的语言的用户) 可以访问视频，你需要在视频内容中包括文本轨道。",
        "text_hash": "46aba296fd86733ba2e0639fb54889331034e37ddd37381bff89ee2b8ee55169",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_745cb74df4d7a6069f5c76f1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "[!NOTE]\n文本轨道对于潜在的任何用户也很有用，而不仅仅是那些残障用户。例如，有些用户可能无法听到音频，因为他们处于嘈杂的环境中 (如显示体育游戏时的拥挤的酒吧),或者如果其他人在安静的地方 (如图书馆),则可能不想打扰其他人。",
        "text_hash": "f3c5771511d06729aa745159117f00eb12f3cc2866f54919db82fdad1a315c5f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "quotation"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a977abe9c1da09eacb53c9f3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这不是一个新概念 ––电视服务已经关闭了字幕相当长的时间了：",
        "text_hash": "b11b43a6f9ced0197112ee8dccafb7e028787dfb62ca1f5c9de5ad0e36e80496",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_477c2225a4460742dd19e35f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Frame from an old-timey cartoon with closed captioning \"Good work, Goldie. Keep it up!\"",
        "text_hash": "c5a26bbff81b61fcd4d9800eafd7250a5d76af5fb00c2ec5a1c08871e1a22685",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_27e06f7a73ba1adc11f09965",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "许多国家/地区提供以英语为母语的字幕的英语电影，例如，DVD 上通常提供不同的语言字幕",
        "text_hash": "9ebf10add8f538da39b61282515651e632b73660f5e676384fb6268c6646bfa6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fd7a948cb2b6239037358abb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "An English film with German subtitles \"Emo, warum erkennst du nicht die Schonheit dieses Ortes?\"",
        "text_hash": "ecf0852441c0e408c03441045e1762e4d8be9fa1a854aa043d07869f2c51e8a2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6d5aa4ae19914f3b932d23e1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "不同类型的文本轨道具有不同的目的。你遇到的主要情况是：",
        "text_hash": "b672a0dae88307b560a77ea88b3365cc26d4198adc8a9439ad75e8b992ccf4cb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_195b7f26de5a7440e981b955",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "标题 ––对于听不到音轨 (包括所讲的单词，还有环境信息，如说话、以及用来营造喜怒气氛的音乐等) 的聋人用户而言是有利的。\n字幕––为不懂所讲语言的用户提供音频对话框的翻译。\n说明–– 这些描述包括无法观看视频的盲人的描述，例如场景的外观。\n章节标题––旨在帮助用户导航媒体资源的章节标记",
        "text_hash": "b45f9d28bc5c44558ff0dc14d826fcc5cac8d400569d22f5d7736da947663b2a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_eeb662ece213f40317615e94",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "实现 HTML5 视频文本轨道",
        "text_hash": "befd91fe69599137834bf5c7b1b40b83c0ee1d88a89d3bb5761148b59d602e6f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_59a44139b3ad35bbe9e9d5d4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "使用 HTML5 视频显示的文本轨道需要用 WebVTT 编写，WebVTT 是一种文本格式，其中包含多个文本字符串以及元数据，例如你希望在视频中显示每个文本字符串的时间，甚至限制样式/定位信息。这些文本字符串称为提示。",
        "text_hash": "ec994e39112cbb79c4917b01ef156faf33170babb47347ff2dd1920faf52d6cf",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_faf214cc48f1786c3e64b1f6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "典型的 WebVTT 文件如下所示：",
        "text_hash": "58a896f764bb791bd30bfe9b065dcee6ada06e90a695d32f6c1698a1761fdbc5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a4c7869e0872641b556713cd",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "plain\nWEBVTT",
        "text_hash": "d2a56e45801b48f9edc0e35b2f29b0c28707c0d376a3f946fa672db044e96e09",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_34b4b754827f05cb4d0b7a74",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "1\n00:00:22.230 --> 00:00:24.606\nThis is the first subtitle.",
        "text_hash": "703c692477cba384330b6d6d2712f03405a9351eb5f7e8173c773666dbe5a9c3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_eaf452841b7174db9bf95e85",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "2\n00:00:30.739 --> 00:00:34.074\nThis is the second.",
        "text_hash": "b32d11185951829204340c1efdd86514a7c9836f872cd1d1df95cfd94caf08d6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_66f73621d1682f39ba9f3904",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "...",
        "text_hash": "ab5df625bc76dbd4e163bed2dd888df828f90159bb93556525c31821b6541d46",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d44ab04a7a175e7678f2c9f1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "要将此信息与 HTML 媒体播放一起显示，你需要：",
        "text_hash": "d2fe73f805bfda000cc791e4b306c9522725c73c7d7928db25216eed38e7368f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_bdbf1f707957848db373e33d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "将其保存为 .vtt 文件，放在一个合理的地方。\n使用  元素链接到 .vtt 文件。  应放在   或   内，但在   元素之后。使用 kind 属性指定提示是字幕、标题还是说明。此外，使用 srclang 告诉浏览器编写字幕所用的语言。",
        "text_hash": "fe8d30983887d7994095972ca588dd6c6c5ddd00972e0eca4cfe575d7e677830",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_425c16d46b40b4946f10e7c8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "下面是一个示例：",
        "text_hash": "48a68e8adc4a6032714892415a0b1f7754f645e2afa609fd79c01d44e4853d25",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5559f3c7676d37c1dc0b05c6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "html",
        "text_hash": "e5e239560bc125a20ff2ac1fea50915bc198dd4f5b5256ec447a8a71e00132b3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e8fe210681be70108363fd81",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "```",
        "text_hash": "f1b901847390b0ed7e374e7c1e464ec17b46a427c487a5ad6cbd2906405083d5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "code"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4619d01ac9ce61dc0f20906d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这将产生显示字幕的视频，如下所示：",
        "text_hash": "35362057958b5aed7e9370bdb429792973e603aeb98b728440241419c66615ab",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a6e472864c9e109ed36c3ec1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Video player with standard controls such as play, stop, volume, and captions on and off. The video playing shows a scene of a man holding a spear-like weapon, and a caption reads \"Esta hoja tiene pasado oscuro.\"",
        "text_hash": "dbdebe3f91dfdd1474c2a7168d77bece08bbab1a01bf54d78033fba25903cf6e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_28f14885aa69f24891156469",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "有关详细信息，请阅读Adding captions and subtitles to HTML5 video。你可以找到与本文一起使用本文的the example,本文由 Ian Devlin 编写 (请参阅source code)。此示例使用一些 JavaScript 允许用户在不同的字幕之间进行选择。请注意，要打开字幕，你需要按\"CC\"按钮并选择一个选项 - 英语、德语或西班牙语。",
        "text_hash": "934e2b6782747c66ef9daeb3ab974bb100d641bfd4db02d0374c9e2c3cdae982",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ed58aca30cc9148f6c67e799",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "[!NOTE]\n文本轨道和转录也可以帮助你使用,因为搜索引擎在文本上尤其繁荣。文本轨道甚至允许搜索引擎通过视频直接链接到一个点部分。",
        "text_hash": "c63011809865fa8e5cbee887cc0eb52561a573a21b65a508b475dc90a7a5d594",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "quotation"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3e0299568332309ba176a14c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "其他多媒体内容",
        "text_hash": "1a78306ac650a6ebb6c2bb4254fcf443b0c4356a696fc3edfd9c54b0381dc79f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e02c1c87426c5fd1c1f104d1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "以上各节未涵盖你可能要放在网页上的所有类型的多媒体内容。你可能还需要处理使用其他可用技术创建的游戏、动画、幻灯片、嵌入式视频和内容，例如：",
        "text_hash": "82855c79a2bc304924eec45b008586155956d5d4676d772415b321bc7eb997ef",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4a3e6599988eed42f195b6df",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "HTML5 canvas\nFlash\nSilverlight",
        "text_hash": "9dee99e37c1f722a00ada6b32233f41bc6b74eaf7cd7ce725963456a283f0d28",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_aad918246f09b4a17f173769",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "对于此类内容，你需要根据案例处理辅助功能问题。在某些情况下，它不是那么糟糕，例如：",
        "text_hash": "d0ad8dbd5a41614b42baba1ba518f77867dc163f559ebcde0230a48246ef8bdd",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d0691096c8d166daf9dc725d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "如果你使用 Flash 或 Silverlight 等插件技术嵌入音频内容，你可能只需以与上面在脚本示例部分中所示的相同方式提供音频脚本。\n如果你使用 Flash 或 Silverlight 等插件技术嵌入视频内容，则可以利用这些技术可用的字幕/字幕技术。例如，参考 Flash captions、Using the Flash-Only Player API for Closed Captioning 或 Playing Subtitles with Videos in Silverlight.",
        "text_hash": "ebfa57aa5993c59da834c4827200871e9ee432d301463860fa10fd58f7ac0de0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6e5c72fc85f7fcb5ca3711ac",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "然而，其他多媒体不是那么容易使访问。例如，如果你正在处理沉浸式 3D 游戏或虚拟现实应用，那么为此类体验提供文本替代方案确实非常困难，你可能会认为盲人用户实际上并不在此类应用的目标受众范围内。",
        "text_hash": "741f9012c0cb0e57926f05a0612e33d9add07c97087d2e0f78974ded33f3ec73",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5eee124341c9688a38cda7e0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "但是，你可以确保此类应用具有足够的颜色对比度和清晰的显示，以便对视力低下/色盲的人来说可以感知，并且还可以使其键盘可访问。请记住，辅助功能就是尽可能多地做，而不是一直追求 100% 的无障碍，这通常是不可能的。",
        "text_hash": "be694c102576a7725ee178034da802a84d39d7dedffbf46af430c564a35383f0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_06d6392ad46de26412694a20",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "总结",
        "text_hash": "04830193b408eeb17c18cfb88440e68061423af6e0c2944c79e4c4cfc6a0f0dc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8d98477c18e33157bc82d2f9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "本章概述了多媒体内容的无障碍问题，以及一些实用的解决方案。",
        "text_hash": "a30969389f4a1b9d0a07c54698e1b14e18d9b2d869292a12474743610ae19636",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_3fe8b1a8a87aaf65175dab66"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
